<p><strong>故事：</strong>最年轻的基金会特工<br />
<strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/douglasliu" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3728730); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3728730&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600569465" alt="DouglasLiu" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3728730)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/douglasliu" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3728730); return false;">DouglasLiu</a></span>，作者页在<strong><a href="/douglasliu-author-page">此</a></strong></p>
